content.question: Expansionary fiscal policy will most likely result in

choices.label: a decrease in the money supply
an increase in the marginal propensity to consume
an increase in nominal interest rates
a decrease in the level of output
a decrease in the price level

content.answer: an increase in nominal interest rates

skill.text: Skill 3.A: Determine the outcome of an economic situation using economic concepts, principles, or models.
